data.description: Welcome to this charming and well-maintained 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that is perfectly situated near a variety of restaurants, shops, parks, and even a walking trail right in front of the property. Enjoy the convenience of having everything you need just a stone's throw away. Plus, with the added bonus of paid-off solar panels, you can enjoy energy-efficient living and lower utility bills. This home truly offers the best of both convenience and comfort - schedule a showing today to see all that it has to offer!
